  <answer><![CDATA[<p><span>The balance of your holiday will be due 10 weeks prior to your holiday departure date. Your credit/debit card used to pay the original deposit will be automatically debited with the balance of your holiday if you accepted this method of payment (this will typically be debited on the Friday after the balance due date). Alternatively, there are a number of alternatives to paying the balance outlined above.</span></p>]]></answer>
